reviewText: We orders this pack but it came with 12 and 13 instead of 11 and twelve. 12 and 13 are both much worst than 11.
Love these movies! The cast is great, the movies are funny and entertaining!

Great movie quality. Good buy. But the description didn't say anything about it only being ONE dvd instead of 2... They may have updated that since I purchased, but I can get over it.

Good movies, people. Quite funny.
Just OK.  Pretty weak but most movies are in this category.  If you like most movies you will probably enjoy this but if you find most to be just marginal you will find this to be the same.

We watched Oceans 11 first, it was on the edge of your seat, whats gonna happen next, an how, great movie... Loved how Clooney an Pitt just knew what they other was gonna say an how they planed out an impossible robbery. The wasy they got all they people involved an the little guy in the change cart... GREAT action!!! I though it was gonna be 3 casinos though Hmmmm..
  we watched Oceans 12 right after an it was just as good loved how all the actors where back an Bruce Willis did a suprise visit... the ending to this movie was very surprising unexpected an awsome picked up right wear 11 left off yet a whole nother story!!! The casino owner from 11 was back an out to get his money only cause some other robber wanted to prove something an it was wonderfull how they keep it a secret an then it all came together....  Iteresting how 11 was about clooney getting a girl back an 12 became about pitt getting a girl.....
